chartSettings.plainMarkdownContent: ### We detected the application **${application}** is enabled for tracing. To see the Spring Boot Trace Browser **[click here](/tracing/search#_v01(tf:!((filterType:Operation,id:0,required:!t,value:!(!(${application}.,${service}.,'*'))))))**.

sectionFilter.query: ts(~component.heartbeat ${filter} and (component="wavefront-generated*" or component="jaeger*" or component="zipkin*")) >= 1
sectionFilter.description: This section will be visible if tracing is enabled.

sources.name: A
sources.query: ts(spring.cloud.gateway.routes.count, source="${source}" AND application="${application}" AND service="${service}" )

sources.name: Success Rates
sources.query: if(exists(${SUCCESS}), ${SUCCESS} / ${TOTAL} * 100, 0)

sources.name: TOTAL
sources.query: sum(ts(spring.cloud.gateway.requests.count, source="${source}" AND application="${application}" AND service="${service}"))

sources.name: SUCCESS
sources.query: sum(ts(spring.cloud.gateway.requests.count, source="${source}" AND application="${application}" AND service="${service}" AND  (httpStatusCode="1*" or httpStatusCode="2*" or httpStatusCode="3*")))

sources.name: Error Rates
sources.query: if (exists(${ERROR}), ${ERROR} / ${TOTAL} * 100, 0)

sources.name: TOTAL
sources.query: sum(ts(spring.cloud.gateway.requests.count, source="${source}" AND application="${application}" AND service="${service}"))

sources.name: ERROR
sources.query: sum(ts(spring.cloud.gateway.requests.count, source="${source}" AND application="${application}" AND service="${service}" AND  (httpStatusCode="4*" or httpStatusCode="5*")))

sources.name: Rate limited Rates
sources.query: ${RATE_LIMITED} / ${TOTAL} * 100

sources.name: RATE_LIMITED
sources.query: sum(ts(spring.cloud.gateway.requests.count, source="${source}" AND application="${application}" AND service="${service}"AND httpStatusCode="429"))

sources.name: TOTAL
sources.query: sum(ts(spring.cloud.gateway.requests.count, source="${source}" AND application="${application}" AND service="${service}"))

sources.name: Average response time
sources.query: rawsum(ts("spring.cloud.gateway.requests.sum", source="${source}" AND application="${application}" AND service="${service}")) / rawsum(ts("spring.cloud.gateway.requests.count", source="${source}" AND application="${application}" AND service="${service}"))

sources.name: Average response time
sources.query: rawavg(join(ts("spring.cloud.gateway.requests.sum", source="${source}" AND application="${application}" AND service="${service}") AS ts1 INNER JOIN ts("spring.cloud.gateway.requests.count", source="${source}" AND application="${application}" AND service="${service}") as ts2 using (httpMethod, path, httpStatusCode), metric='averageResponsePerRoute', httpMethod=ts1.httpMethod, httpStatusCode=ts1.httpStatusCode, path=ts1.path, requestsSum=ts1.value, requestsCount=ts2.value, ts1 / ts2), httpMethod, path)

sources.name: A
sources.query: rawmax(ts("spring.cloud.gateway.requests.max", source="${source}" AND application="${application}" AND service="${service}").gt(0))

sources.name: A
sources.query: rawmax(ts("spring.cloud.gateway.requests.max", source="${source}" AND application="${application}" AND service="${service}").gt(0), httpMethod, path)

sources.name: API usage
sources.query: sum(ts("spring.cloud.gateway.requests.count", source="${source}" AND application="${application}" AND service="${service}"))

sources.name: API usage
sources.query: sum(ts("spring.cloud.gateway.requests.count", source="${source}" AND application="${application}" AND service="${service}") by (path, httpMethod))

sources.name: API usage
sources.query: sum(ts("spring.cloud.gateway.requests.count", source="${source}" AND application="${application}" AND service="${service}") by(httpMethod, path))

sources.name: API usage
sources.query: sum(ts("spring.cloud.gateway.requests.count", source="${source}" AND application="${application}" AND service="${service}" AND (httpStatusCode="4*" or httpStatusCode="5*")))

sources.name: API usage
sources.query: sum(ts("spring.cloud.gateway.requests.count", source="${source}" AND application="${application}" AND service="${service}" AND  (httpStatusCode="4*" or httpStatusCode="5*")) by (path, httpMethod))

sources.name: API usage
sources.query: sum(ts("spring.cloud.gateway.requests.count", source="${source}" AND application="${application}" AND service="${service}" AND (httpStatusCode="4*" or httpStatusCode="5*")) by(httpMethod, path))

sources.name: Successful authentications by path
sources.query: sum(ts("spring.cloud.gateway.requests.count", source="${source}" AND application="${application}" AND service="${service}" AND hasAuthenticationFilter="true" AND  (httpStatusCode="1*" or httpStatusCode="2*" or httpStatusCode="3*")) by(httpMethod, path))

sources.name: Forbidden Error Path by rate
sources.query: sum(ts("spring.cloud.gateway.requests.count", source="${source}" AND application="${application}" AND service="${service}" AND httpStatusCode="403") by (path, httpMethod)) / sum(ts("spring.cloud.gateway.requests.count", source="${source}" AND application="${application}" AND service="${service}") by (path, httpMethod)) * 100

sources.name: Unsuccessful authentications by path
sources.query: sum(ts("spring.cloud.gateway.requests.count", source="${source}" AND application="${application}" AND service="${service}" AND httpStatusCode="401") by (path, httpMethod)) / sum(ts("spring.cloud.gateway.requests.count", source="${source}" AND application="${application}" AND service="${service}") by (path, httpMethod)) * 100
